Title: Men’s Bird Illustration Tee
Body (HTML):
We are huge fans of AS Colour tees—and not just because they’re source from a fantastic New Zealand company!

In fact, as an experiment, we have worn these tees alongside 4 other leading brands for 6 months—and we can confidently say AS Colour tees are hands-down the best!

Some of the Lucid team still wear AS Colour tees we made over 7 years ago and they have held their prints and are still looking good!

Specs

  • Regular fit
  • Crew neck
  • 180gsm / 5.3 oz/y² mid-weight
  • 100% combed cotton
  • Neck ribbing, side seamed, shoulder to shoulder tape, double needle hems, preshrunk to minimise shrinkage

Title: Pocket Notebook
Body (HTML):
One can never have too many notebooks!

At 89 × 127 mm (3.5 × 5 in), they’re perfect for keeping next to the keyboard or carrying in a pocket or bag.

Made with care using 100% recycled papers and vegetable-oil based inks in Portland, Oregon.
